{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"radius","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/radius","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考主页</a></p>\n\n<p><code>radius</code>属性代表了一个给定<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a>滤镜上的操作。如果提供了两个<a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#number\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Paint\">&lt;number&gt;</a>，则第一个数代表了 x-radius，第二个数代表了 y-radius。如果只提供了一个数字，则值同时用于 x 和 y。值是在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/filter\"><code>&lt;filter&gt;</code></a> 元素的属性<code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/primitiveUnits\">primitiveUnits</a></code> 确定的坐标系统内。</p>\n\n<p>如果没有指定该属性值，效果等同于指定了一个<strong>0</strong>值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td><em>无</em></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Content_type#number-optional-number\" title=\"en/SVG/Content_type#Paint\">&lt;number-optional-number&gt;</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feMorphologyRadiusAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下元素可以使用<code>radius</code>属性：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMorphology\"><code>&lt;feMorphology&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考主页","popularity":